thread.title: AlphaOne to host open Body-Building Championship

author: timesofindia.indiatimes.com
title: AlphaOne to host open Body-Building Championship
text:
AMRITSAR: AlphaOne in association with Northern Strength Building Federation of India and Royal Enfield will host the 3rd Open Body-Building Championship 2015, on Sunday, The event will be part of their 'Be The Change Club', initiative with the slogan of 'Say Yes to Health and Say No to Drugs.'
Over 170 participants have registered in 4 categories including, Overall Strength Building, Bench-Press, Push-ups and Best Biceps Championship. Dr. Prodipta Sen of Alpha G:Corp expressed his satisfaction with the collaboration for this event between AlphaOne and Northern Strength Building Federation of India as well as Royal Enfield.
"The Open Body Building Championship is an annual event that we started 3 years back under our Amritsar Sparkling and Be The Change Club initiative to encourage the youth towards overall body health and to spread awareness against drug addiction. We feel proud of every contribution we can make in fostering a healthy and aware society. We will continue to aim for optimum customer and community delight with many such events," Eom said in a statement.
